Package com.commander4j.db

Class JDBDataIDs

java.lang.Object
com.commander4j.db.JDBDataIDs
public class JDBDataIDs extends Object
JDBDataIDs class is used to insert/update/delete the APP_MATERIAL_DATA_IDS table. The default APP_MATERIAL table holds the basic material master data. However in order to extend the type of data which can be stored and also link it so a customer there is another table called APP_MATERIAL_CUSTOMER_DATA. This second table is keyed on MATERIAL, CUSTOMER_ID and DATA_ID. The DATA_ID can be anything meaningful name to describe the new data item being stored.
